{"tid":1616481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好懶 繁體字幕要有 !","createTime":"2019-10-03T12:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:51:57.000Z","uid":279799,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"353ae5fbebe163122e5f60f3e7753742558807b0","tid":1616481,"uid":279799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"(代放 如圖)<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月黎除左自己人外 相信最關注我地之一就係台灣市民<br />\n不過因為佢地 (尤其係老一輩) 唔係好聽得明廣東話 好多時候又得英文字幕 所以就算見到片想睇都聽唔明睇唔明我地講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忽略佢地既需要 因為最能明白我地既就係對岸既台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋繁體字幕 將克警既彪炳戰績spread到全世界都知 謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n期待煲底除罩相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N95o8vE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN95o8vE.jpg&h=8936669e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uw138vF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUw138vF.jpg&h=18fa8f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4a8d921be8e5434ac3755156df2054015d2a8d9","tid":1616481,"uid":304834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfb1a5b95c9198e0c9f19c1c6f4039753917567","tid":1616481,"uid":111658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"推 對外文宣要做足"},{"pid":"a047ad738a12015cb1e9167bb2dc146f3a0e88b7","tid":1616481,"uid":200492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T12:43:14.000Z","msg":"推 文宣組幫手做野"},{"pid":"1a7e5430aa3f5325cd3cf6b63153b509e9abd753","tid":1616481,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"